OL,6,GWe are Foundry Zero. We love making
OL,7,Gthings and taking things apart, and
OL,8,Gwe're delighted to be sponsoring EMF
OL,9,G2026! We're running a small reverse
OL,10,Gengineering CTF, a radio challenge and
OL,11,Ga set of challenges for kids at our
OL,12,Gvillage. If you're interested in
OL,13,Gcareers in Cyber Security, or just
OL,14,Gmessing around in some binary
OL,15,Gchallenges, come see us any time over
OL,16,Gthe weekend.
